<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Voice Fantasia is a video game RPG published in 1997 for PlayStation by ASK Kodansha and the game is also avaliable for the Saturn console.
                  <br><br>The game features three cute girls as main characters solving a quest. The graphics of the game were dated already by 1997 and so it heavily stressed on voice acting.
                  <br><br>There was a lot of spoken parts albeit not all the actors were famous by the time the game was made. Yui Horie also started her career as a voice actress in this game.
                  <br><br>STORY:
                  <br>The player's character is a young boy that lives in our world when someday a strange man appears and give him a new video game, when he returns home and put the game in his console a princess appear in the TV screen and ask him to help her save her kingdom, after that a hand appear and grab him through the TV screen and he appears in the princess world where he encounters one of the game 3 heroines (the wizard girl).
                  <br><br>She takes him to a restuarant and when they are there they see a blonde magician that leaves the restaurant before them and when they are going to leave they have to pay his doubts there and got to wash the dishes, after that they discover where he lives and the game quest will begin there.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Being deployed in a live-action and animated fantasy adventure of the voice actors also appeared popular. Animation by day, night and live action, the game locked in a world where three heroines have to save it, the hero was summoned to the world is different from searching for clues in their conversation, she found the door of the solution so.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Medieval Fantasy theme.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

